33\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">Bundles with dock, case, or box perform better.</p><h3 data-section-id=\"kbqnaq\" data-start=\"2435\" data-end=\"2446\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Trust</h3><p data-start=\"2447\" data-end=\"2509\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">Professional listings sell faster than cheap but unclear ones.</p><hr data-start=\"2511\" data-end=\"2514\" style=\"font-size: medium;\"><h2 data-section-id=\"zgd3qt\" data-start=\"2516\" data-end=\"2552\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Is It Still Profitable to Resell?</h2><p data-start=\"2554\" data-end=\"2603\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">The Steam Deck is no longer a quick flip product.</p><p data-start=\"2605\" data-end=\"2627\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">But it still works as:</p><ul data-start=\"2629\" data-end=\"2719\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\"><li data-section-id=\"1vb9rz1\" data-start=\"2629\" data-end=\"2653\">A stable resale item</li><li data-section-id=\"l84mg8\" data-start=\"2654\" data-end=\"2677\">A consistent seller</li><li data-section-id=\"oe5wns\" data-start=\"2678\" data-end=\"2719\">A good product for long term business</li></ul><hr data-start=\"2721\" data-end=\"2724\" style=\"font-size: medium;\"><h2 data-section-id=\"hutdt9\" data-start=\"2726\" data-end=\"2761\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Who Is Buying Steam Decks Today?</h2><p data-start=\"2763\" data-end=\"2788\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">Most buyers are informed:</p><ul data-start=\"2790\" data-end=\"2863\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\"><li data-section-id=\"1v5qx6c\" data-start=\"2790\" data-end=\"2803\">PC gamers</li><li data-section-id=\"1obgd1b\" data-start=\"2804\" data-end=\"2824\">Tech enthusiasts</li><li data-section-id=\"e21p5b\" data-start=\"2825\" data-end=\"2863\">People looking for portable gaming</li></ul><p data-start=\"2865\" data-end=\"2923\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">They compare listings and choose quality over cheap deals.</p><hr data-start=\"2925\" data-end=\"2928\" style=\"font-size: medium;\"><h2 data-section-id=\"qjyped\" data-start=\"2930\" data-end=\"2945\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Final Answer</h2><p data-start=\"2947\" data-end=\"3002\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">Steam Deck resale prices now reflect real market value:</p><ul data-start=\"3004\" data-end=\"3114\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\"><li data-section-id=\"10iap0q\" data-start=\"3004\" data-end=\"3042\">Budget models attract entry buyers</li><li data-section-id=\"9jns2n\" data-start=\"3043\" data-end=\"3076\">Mid range models sell fastest</li><li data-section-id=\"ivx906\" data-start=\"3077\" data-end=\"3114\">OLED models command higher prices</li></ul><p data-start=\"3116\" data-end=\"3247\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">The <strong data-start=\"3120\" data-end=\"3161\">Valve Steam Deck</strong> remains one of the few gaming devices that still holds strong resale value over time.</p>",
